Richard L. Clemmer: Executive Profile & Biography - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 22, 2017 11:47 AM ET
Semiconductors and Semiconductor Equipment

Company Overview of NXP Semiconductors N.V.



SnapshotPeople 




OverviewBoard MembersCommittees



Executive Profile
Richard L. Clemmer  Chief Executive Officer, President and Executive Director, NXP Semiconductors N.V.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 4 Board Members in 4 different organizations across 9 different industries.See Board Relationships66$17,934,560As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. Richard L. Clemmer, also known as Rick, has been Chief Executive Officer and President of NXP Semiconductors NV since January 1, 2009. Mr. Clemmer serves as Chief Executive Officer and President at NXP B.V since January 1, 2009. Mr. Clemmer served as the Head of Global Sales and Marketing at NXP Semiconductors N.V since July 2011. He served as a Senior Advisor at Kohlberg Kravis Roberts & Co. since June 13, 2007. He was Partner at Shelter Capital Partners. He serves ... as an Advisor of Jetalon Solutions, Inc. He drove the turnaround and re-emergence of Agere Systems Inc., a spin-out from Lucent Technologies Inc. He served as Senior Vice President of Texas Instruments Incorporated. He has over 30 years of experience in the technology industry, where he has held a variety of executive, financial and management positions. His experience includes operations control and finance, strategic acquisitions and structuring, capital fund-raising, investor relations and international operations. Mr. Clemmer served as the President and Chief Executive Officer of Agere Systems Inc., since October 26, 2005. He served as the Chairman and President of Venture Capital Technology LLC since mid-2003. He served as the Chief Executive Officer and President of PurchasePro.com Inc. since June 2001 and as its Chief Financial Officer from May 2001 to September 2001 and again since May 3, 2002. Mr. Clemmer has held executive leadership positions in high technology industries including Semiconductors, Storage, Disk Drives, e-Commerce and Software industries. Prior to joining PurchasePro, Mr. Clemmer served as an Executive Vice President of Finance and Chief Financial Officer of Quantum Corporation, Hard Disk Drive Group from August 1996 to May 2001. He served as Secretary and Chief Accounting Officer of Quantum Corporation. He served as the Chief Financial Officer, Secretary and Executive Vice President of Finance at Quantum Corp. He served as Senior Vice President and Chief Finance Officer of the Semiconductor Group at Texas Instruments Inc. from 1988 to 1996. He served as the Chairman of the Board and a Member of the Board of Directors at U-NAV Microelectronics Corporation until December 2005. He served as the Chairman of the Board of PurchasePro.com Inc. since June 4, 2002 and Vice Chairman from June 2001 to June 4, 2002. He has been an Executive Director of NXP Semiconductors N.V. since January 1, 2009.  He serves as a Director of Jetalon Solutions, Inc. He has been Executive Director of NXP B.V. since January 1, 2009.  He has been a Director of NCR Corporation since April 23, 2008, Trident Microsystems Inc. since February 2010.  He served as a Director of i2 Technologies Inc., since June 2004. He served as a Non-Executive Director of Oxford Semiconductor Inc. He served as a Director at Agere Systems Inc., since October 2002. He served as a Director of Cantata Technology Inc. and PurchasePro.com Inc. He served as a Member of Advisory Board of ePolicy Solutions, Inc. He served as a Member of Board of Management and Chairman of Board of Management of NXP B.V. from December 1, 2007 to December 31, 2008. He holds a Master's in Business Administration from Southern Methodist University and a BA in Business Administration from Texas Tech University.Read Full Background




